        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2411579152" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer13992499164601630881">The Restorer by Sharon Hinck is told from the point of view of a soccer mum who is sucked into a fantasy world, which I thought would be right up my alley, but while it was an enjoyable story, I found it a little slow. That may have had something to do with the fact that I was reading a copy with bonus scenes included, but maybe not, as a lot of the exposition was told, rather than shown, which I think was one reason why I found it difficult to engage in the novel. However, if you like Christian</span>
  <span id="freeText13992499164601630881" style="display:none">The Restorer by Sharon Hinck is told from the point of view of a soccer mum who is sucked into a fantasy world, which I thought would be right up my alley, but while it was an enjoyable story, I found it a little slow. That may have had something to do with the fact that I was reading a copy with bonus scenes included, but maybe not, as a lot of the exposition was told, rather than shown, which I think was one reason why I found it difficult to engage in the novel. However, if you like Christian speculative fiction (and it's HEAVILY Christian) then you may well enjoy this one.</span>
  <a data-text-id="13992499164601630881" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

