        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer466504522" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer14034210225327661947">I was surprised at how much I liked this book. Christian fiction with a fantasy twist that didn&apos;t annoy the ever loving crap out of me. Definitely a great recommendation for someone who wants to get into the genre, but doesn&apos;t want to be bashed over the head with the Bible thumping. </span>
  <span id="freeText14034210225327661947" style="display:none">I was surprised at how much I liked this book. Christian fiction with a fantasy twist that didn't annoy the ever loving crap out of me. Definitely a great recommendation for someone who wants to get into the genre, but doesn't want to be bashed over the head with the Bible thumping. </span>
