<div id="review_2064993576" class="review nosyndicate" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/2064993576" />
    <a title="Sharon" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/26173369-sharon"><img alt="Sharon" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1387434936p2/26173369.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/2064993576?book_show_action=true">Jul 18, 2017</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Sharon" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Sharon" href="/user/show/26173369-sharon">Sharon</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Kindle Edition " href="/book/show/13022812-the-restorer">review of another edition</a>


        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2064993576" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer10236641092367563345">The first chapter is deceptively benign until the last few paragraphs give a hint of the out of this world adventure ahead. From then on it is quite a wild ride through an alternate universe. This book offers quite a lot of gems… warrior heroes, strong heroines, hints of romance, fierce battles, suspense, evil plots, sparring (both literal and verbal), miracles, and so much more. The ending is not really an ending but the launch for Book 2.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


      <div class="reviewFooter uitext buttons">
          

