      <div class=" clearFloats bigBox"><div class="h2Container gradientHeaderContainer"><h2 class="brownBackground"><a href="/trivia/work/755010-the-restorer-the-sword-of-lyric-1">Trivia About The Restorer (The...</a></h2></div><div class="bigBoxBody"><div class="bigBoxContent containerWithHeaderContent">
        <div class="mediumText">No trivia or quizzes yet. <a href="/trivia/work/755010-the-restorer-the-sword-of-lyric-1">Add some now &raquo;</a></div>
